name: Gold Historical Prices
content:
Description: Dataset about gold prices from 1979-2024

[Source](https://www.gold.org/goldhub/data/gold-prices)
* Data was processed to remove commas from numerical values over 1000

Columns:

* Date (string): Date in MM/DD/YYYY format of the day the price of gold was recorded
* United States Dollar (number): the price of gold in United States Dollars
* Euro (number): the price of gold in Euros
* Euro (number): the price of gold in Euros
